<div class="c-shop-login-register-1" style="padding:5% 0;">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6" style="text-align:center;">
      <script src="https://unpkg.com/@dotlottie/player-component@latest/dist/dotlottie-player.mjs" type="module"></script>
      <dotlottie-player src="https://lottie.host/31b7ea34-dec1-4a45-ac46-8fcc7c56245d/24fV3coqIw.json" background="transparent" speed="1" style="width: 300px; height: 300px;margin:auto;" loop="" autoplay="" class="svg-element"></dotlottie-player>
      {% if ('/fr/' in url)  %}
      <h2>Vous n'êtes pas encore inscrit ?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;text-align:center;">Inscrivez-vous aujourd'hui pour recevoir <b>une réduction exclusive de 15 %</b> sur votre première commande. Rejoignez notre réseau et restez à la pointe de l'innovation biotechnologique.</p>
      {% elseif ('/es/' in url)  %}
      <h2>¿Aún no te has registrado?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;text-align:center;">Regístrese hoy para recibir un descuento <b>exclusivo del 15 %</b> en su primer pedido. Únase a nuestra red y manténgase a la vanguardia de la innovación biotecnológica.</p>
      {% elseif ('/cn/' in url)  %}
      <h2>你还没有注册吗？</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;text-align:center;">立即註冊即可享有首筆訂單 15% 的獨家折扣。加入我們的網路並保持在生物技術創新的最前沿。</p>
      {% elseif ('/de/' in url)  %}
      <h2>Noch nicht angemeldet?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;text-align:center;">Registrieren Sie sich noch heute, um einen <b>exklusiven Rabatt von 15 %</b> auf Ihre erste Bestellung zu erhalten. Treten Sie unserem Netzwerk bei und bleiben Sie an der Spitze der Biotech-Innovation.</p>

      {% elseif ('/ja/' in url)  %}
      <h2>まだ登録していませんか？</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;text-align:center;">今すぐ登録して、初回注文で 15% の特別割引を受けましょう。当社のネットワークに参加して、バイオテクノロジーのイノベーションの最前線に立ち続けましょう。</p>

      {% else %}
      <h2>Haven't signed up yet?</h2>
      <p style="font-size:14px;text-align:center;">Register today to receive an <b>exclusive 15% discount</b> on your first order. Join our network and stay at the forefront of biotech innovation.</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="c-form-register">
        {% if ('/fr/' in url)  %}
        <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link btn-medium btn btn-mod c-btn c-theme-btn c-font-bold c-font-uppercase c-font-white button js-form-submit form-submit">{{ 'Créez votre compte'|t }}</a>.
        {% elseif ('/es/' in url)  %}
        <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link btn-medium btn btn-mod c-btn c-theme-btn c-font-bold c-font-uppercase c-font-white button js-form-submit form-submit">{{ 'Crea tu cuenta'|t }}</a>.
        {% elseif ('/cn/' in url)  %}
        <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link btn-medium btn btn-mod c-btn c-theme-btn c-font-bold c-font-uppercase c-font-white button js-form-submit form-submit">{{ '创建您的帐户'|t }}</a>.
        {% elseif ('/de/' in url)  %}
        <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link btn-medium btn btn-mod c-btn c-theme-btn c-font-bold c-font-uppercase c-font-white button js-form-submit form-submit">{{ 'Erstellen Sie Ihr Konto'|t }}</a>.

        {% elseif ('/ja/' in url)  %}
        <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link btn-medium btn btn-mod c-btn c-theme-btn c-font-bold c-font-uppercase c-font-white button js-form-submit form-submit">{{ 'アカウントを作成する'|t }}</a>.


        {% else %}
        <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link btn-medium btn btn-mod c-btn c-theme-btn c-font-bold c-font-uppercase c-font-white button js-form-submit form-submit">{{ 'Create Your Account'|t }}</a>.
        {% endif %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="panel panel-default c-panel">
        <div class="panel-body c-panel-body">
          {% if ('/fr/' in url)  %}
          <h1 style="text-align:center;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;">Vous avez oublié votre mot de passe ?</h1>
          <div style="margin:5% 0;">
          {{ rendered }}
          </div>
          <a href="https://norgenbiotek.com/fr/user/login">Retour à la connexion</a>
          {% elseif ('/es/' in url)  %}
          <h1 style="text-align:center;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;">¿Olvidaste tu contraseña?</h1>
          <div style="margin:5% 0;">
          {{ rendered }}
          </div>
          <a href="https://norgenbiotek.com/es/user/login">Volver a iniciar sesión</a>
          {% elseif ('/cn/' in url)  %}
          <h1 style="text-align:center;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;">忘记密码了吗？</h1>
          <div style="margin:5% 0;">
          {{ rendered }}
          </div>
          <a href="https://norgenbiotek.com/cn/user/login">重新登录</a>
          {% elseif ('/de/' in url)  %}
          <h1 style="text-align:center;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;">Passwort vergessen?</h1>
          <div style="margin:5% 0;">
          {{ rendered }}
          </div>
          <a href="https://norgenbiotek.com/de/user/login">Zurück zur Anmeldung</a>

          {% elseif ('/ja/' in url)  %}
          <h1 style="text-align:center;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;">パスワードをお忘れですか？</h1>
          <div style="margin:5% 0;">
          {{ rendered }}
          </div>
          <a href="https://norgenbiotek.com/ja/user/login">ログインに戻る</a>


          {% else %}
          <h1 style="text-align:center;font-size:30px;font-weight:600;">Forgot Your Password?</h1>
          <div style="margin:5% 0;">
          {{ rendered }}
          </div>
          <a href="https://norgenbiotek.com/user/login">Back To Login</a>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% if toggle_checkbox %}
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="panel panel-default c-panel">
          <div class="panel-body c-panel-body">
            <div class="c-content-title-1">
              <h3 class="c-left">
                <i class="icon-user"></i>{{ 'Don\'t have an account yet?'|t }}</h3>
              <div class="c-line-left c-theme-bg"></div>
              <p>{{ 'Join us and enjoy shopping online today.'|t }}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="c-margin-fix">
              {{ toggle_checkbox }}
            </div>
            <div class="c-form-register">
              <a href="{{ url('user.register') }}" class="c-theme-link">{{ 'User Register Form'|t }}</a>.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</div>

<style>
#block-jango-primary-local-tasks{
  display:none;
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 992px) {
  .c-shop-login-register-1 > .row > div{
    margin:5px 0 0;
  }
}
@media only screen and (max-width: 315px) {
  .svg-element{
    width:100px !important;
    height:100px !important;
  }
  .js-form-submit.form-submit{
        width: auto;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
}
.c-shop-login-register-1 .form-control.input-lg{
  border-radius:4px !important;
}
</style>